<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>数据库备份通知</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', Arial, sans-serif;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background-color: #f4f4f4; padding: 40px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table role="presentation" width="600" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
          <tr>
            <td style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;">
              <h1 style="margin: 0; color: #ffffff; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600;">数据库备份通知</h1>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px 30px;">
              <p style="margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 16px; color: #333; line-height: 1.6;">
                尊敬的 <strong style="color: #667eea;">{{name}}</strong>，您好！
              </p>
              <p style="margin: 0 0 30px; font-size: 16px; color: #666; line-height: 1.6;">
                系统已完成数据库自动备份，备份文件已作为附件发送，请查收。
              </p>
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 30px;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding: 20px;">
                    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                      <tr>
                        <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">备份日期：</td>
                        <td style="padding: 8px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #333; font-weight: 500;">{{backupDate}}</td>
                      </tr>
                    </table>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #999; text-align: center;">
                请妥善保管备份文件，注意数据安全
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; border-top: 1px solid #eee;">
              <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #999; text-align: center;">
                此邮件由系统自动发送，请勿直接回复
              </p>
              <p style="margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 14px; color: #999; text-align: center;">
                © 2024 易旅客 All Rights Reserved
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
